<div class="noinclude"><span class="script">template.XULRefElem()</span></div>
<p>A group of radio buttons. Only one radio button inside the group can be selected at a time. The <span class="script">template.XULElem("radio")</span> buttons may either direct children of the <code>radiogroup</code> or descendants. Place the <code>radiogroup</code> inside a <span class="script">template.XULElem("groupbox")</span> if you would like a border or <span class="script">template.XULElem("caption")</span> for the group. The <code>radiogroup</code> defaults to vertical orientation.</p>
<p>More information is available in the <a title="en/XUL_Tutorial/Input_Controls" href="/en/XUL_Tutorial/Input_Controls">XUL tutorial</a>.</p>
